==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exemplarily
<hw>Ex"em*pla*ri*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a manner
fitted or designed to be an example for imitation or for warning; by way
of example.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>She is <qex>exemplarily</qex> loyal.</q>
<rj><qau>Howell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some he punisheth <qex>exemplarily</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Hakewill.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exemplariness</ent>⟦br⟧
